==美國==
[[File:100th_meridian_US.svg|thumb]]與[[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]的部份邊界以西經100度線為主。（紅線部份）]]

於[[美國|美國]]，西經100度線是{{le|德克薩斯州鍋柄狀地區|Texas panhandle}}與[[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]的邊界，該邊界依據1819年時[[新西班牙副王區|新西班牙副王區]]與美國簽訂的[[亞當斯-奧尼斯條約|亞當斯-奧尼斯條約]]中以[[紅河_(密西西比河)|紅河]]、[[阿肯色河|阿肯色河]]、西經100度線為界轉變而來。<ref name="Danver2013">{{cite book | language  = en |first=Steven L. |last=Danver |title=Encyclopedia of Politics of the American West |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UCRzAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA147 |date=2013-05-14 |publisher=SAGE Publications |isbn=978-1-4522-7606-9 |page=147 |access-date=2016-01-04 |archive-date=2019-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604121413/https://books.google.com/books?id=UCRzAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA147 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[道奇城_(堪薩斯州)|道奇城]]位於阿肯色河流域上，並且非常接近西經100度線（{{Coord|37|45|35|N|100|01|06|W|}}）。<ref>{{cite web | language  = en | title = Dodge City, Kansas | url = https://latitude.to/articles-by-country/us/united-states/3543/dodge-city-kansas | website = latitude.to | access-date = 2022-04-11 | archive-date = 2022-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220411160718/https://latitude.to/articles-by-country/us/united-states/3543/dodge-city-kansas | dead-url = no }}</ref>

於[[北美大平原|北美大平原]]，西經100度線是從[[墨西哥灣|墨西哥灣]]而來的潮濕空氣所約略能抵達北美中部的西邊界線<ref>{{cite magazine | language  = en | first = Shannon | last = Hall | title = A Nation Divided: Arid/Humid Climate Boundary in U.S. Creeps Eastward | url = https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/a-nation-divided-arid-humid-climate-boundary-in-u-s-creeps-eastward/ | publisher = [[科学美国人|Scientific American]]  | date = 2018-04-27 | access-date = 2022-04-22 | archive-date = 2022-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220215004050/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/a-nation-divided-arid-humid-climate-boundary-in-u-s-creeps-eastward/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並且大約是[[半乾旱氣候|半乾旱氣候]]（在某些區域該邊界會稍微東移）與[[溫帶大陸性濕潤氣候|溫帶大陸性濕潤氣候]]（約北緯40度線以北）、[[副熱帶濕潤氣候|副熱帶濕潤氣候]]（約北緯40度線以南）的氣候界線。西經100度線以西的美國地區<ref>{{cite book | language  = en | first1 = Rudi | last1 = Hartmann | first2 = Jing'ai | last2 = Wang | first3 = Tao | last3 = Ye | title = A Comparative Geography of China and the U.S. |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=KfUsBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA34&lpg=PA34&dq=40++parallel+humid+continental++humid+subtropical&source=bl&ots=rFboug0dvr&sig=ACfU3U2mS-RKYwhmOYw58TVtkNpikIAQAQ&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjp5-Dg3af3AhUPpVYBHdgFBUMQ6AF6BAghEAM#v=onepage&q=40%20%20parallel%20humid%20continental%20%20humid%20subtropical&f=false | year = 2014 | publisher = Springer | isbn = 9789401787925 | page=34 }}</ref>，在[[農業|農業]]上非常依賴[[灌溉|灌溉]]。在歷史上，西經100度線經常被認為是美國東部與西部的粗略邊界。<ref>{{cite magazine | language  = en | first = Harvey | last = Leifert | title = Dividing line: The past, present and future of the 100th Meridian | url = https://www.earthmagazine.org/article/dividing-line-past-present-and-future-100th-meridian/ | publisher = EARTH Magazine | date = 2018-01-09 | access-date = 2022-04-11 | archive-date = 2022-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220328233646/https://www.earthmagazine.org/article/dividing-line-past-present-and-future-100th-meridian/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[南北戰爭|南北戰爭]]後的1870年代，美國白人向西擴展定居點至西經100度線左右。<ref>{{cite book | language  = en | author = Washington State Historical Society | title = The Pacific Northwest Quarterly |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=57Q3AQAAIAAJ&pg=PA118&dq=White+settlement+westward++1870s+100+meridian&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwipv6ySwa73AhVQx2EKHazRC-AQ6AF6BAgEEAI#v=onepage&q=White%20settlement%20westward%20%201870s%20100%20meridian&f=false | year = 1908 | publisher = University of Washington | isbn =  | page=118 }}</ref>

位於[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]]{{le|科扎德|Cozad, Nebraska}}的[[30號美國國道|30號美國國道]]上，設立西經100度線標幟，象徵該地為[[奧勒岡小徑|奧勒岡小徑]]、[[驛馬快信制|驛馬快信制]]、[[第一條橫貫大陸鐵路|第一條橫貫大陸鐵路]]、{{le|林肯高速公路|Lincoln Highway}}等重要美國東西交通相交地點。<ref>{{cite book | language  = en | first1 = Jody L. | last1 = Lamp | first2 = Melody | last2 = Dobson | title = History of Nebraska Agriculture, A: A Life Worth Living |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=ow7iDgAAQBAJ&dq=U.S.+Highway+30+++Cozad+meridian++Oregon+Trail+Pony+Express+transcontinental+railroad&hl=zh-TW&source=gbs_navlinks_s | year = 2017 | publisher = Arcadia Publishing | isbn = 9781467136495 | page = 134-135 }}</ref>

==大眾文化==
